name: GotNew
tag_list: events, tickets, map, social, share, location, geo
description: Location based service to find events
overview:
GotNew! is a free 411 service to find tickets and directions to concerts, musicals and sports events close to you. It uses user’s location stored with a Geo-Location service like Yahoo or from user’s IP address. Users do not need to type their location, which is great on a mobile phone like iPhone.

Users can share interesting events with their friends on popular social networks like Twitter, Facebook and MySpace with a single click of a button.

Users can purchase tickets on the searched events by linking with a single click to the event on the TicketMaster’s site. For example, try it for the Jonas Brothers Concert searched at gotnew.com: http://gotnew.com/near-events/tickets.php?shr=&loc=95113%2C+US&kwd=Jonas+Brothers .
